flowchart LR
  S[Canonical state: direct runner state and transcript]
  M[Invoke current model]
  D{Interpret model result}
  H[Apply handoff]
  T[Execute structured tool calls]
  R[Append ordered tool results]
  F[Final output]
  X[Bounded failure]

  S --> M
  M --> D
  D -->|handoff| H
  H --> S
  D -->|tool calls| T
  T --> R
  R --> S
  D -->|final| F
  M -. turn, retry, timeout, cancellation limits .-> X
